-And Jin-woo can't even drink much.

495
00:21:14,106 --> 00:21:15,941
Look how quickly Han-ju's walking.

496
00:21:16,024 --> 00:21:17,859
-Go ahead and put on those aprons.
-Okay.

497
00:21:19,194 --> 00:21:20,654
This looks tricky to put on.

498
00:21:22,614 --> 00:21:24,366
Let me know if you need any help.

499
00:21:24,992 --> 00:21:27,160
-How do you do this?
-You pull it like this.

500
00:21:29,871 --> 00:21:31,206
Then, tie it at the back.

501
00:21:31,290 --> 00:21:32,624
<i>Help each other out.</i>

502
00:21:32,708 --> 00:21:34,042
<i>Yes, help each other!</i>

503
00:21:36,503 --> 00:21:37,504
Can you help me?

504
00:21:37,587 --> 00:21:39,339
-I'll help you.
-Yes, please.

505
00:21:39,423 --> 00:21:40,757
-How do you do this?
-Let's see.

506
00:21:45,470 --> 00:21:46,471
-Turn around.
-Okay.

507
00:21:47,639 --> 00:21:49,016
<i>She's taking care of him</i>
<i>like a little brother.</i>

508
00:21:49,099 --> 00:21:50,726
<i>Yeah, but it's not bad at all.</i>

509
00:21:52,394 --> 00:21:53,603
You're a handful.

510
00:21:53,687 --> 00:21:55,772
You seem like such a mature lady today.

511
00:21:56,857 --> 00:22:01,153
In this short session,
you'll make a drink of your own.

512
00:22:01,236 --> 00:22:05,198
We'll begin with a tasting of six gins.

513
00:22:05,282 --> 00:22:06,783
Can you handle six?

514
00:22:07,993 --> 00:22:08,827
I'm not sure.

515
00:22:09,494 --> 00:22:10,954
What if I get wasted?

516
00:22:11,872 --> 00:22:13,332
Will I need to carry you on my back?

517
00:22:14,374 --> 00:22:16,793
This is Malfy gin from Italy.

518
00:22:19,463 --> 00:22:20,839
Please don't drink it, Han-ju.

519
00:22:21,465 --> 00:22:23,508
-Orange?
-It's orangey, right?

520
00:22:24,509 --> 00:22:25,635
That's strong.

521
00:22:25,719 --> 00:22:26,720
Is it?

522
00:22:27,846 --> 00:22:29,973
Just take a sip, and in front of you…

523
00:22:30,974 --> 00:22:32,559
You look way too excited.

524
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:40,901
Strong, isn't it?

525
00:22:42,444 --> 00:22:45,489
This is Bombay Bramble.

526
00:22:51,328 --> 00:22:52,788
-Oh, no.
-This is called Monkey 47…

527
00:22:52,871 --> 00:22:54,456
-Han-ju.
-The amount she's sipping…

528
00:22:57,793 --> 00:22:59,586
-Are you drinking it?
-I am, but it's a bit…

529
00:22:59,669 --> 00:23:01,088
-Just smell it.
-Just the smell.

530
00:23:01,171 --> 00:23:03,006
Take your own advice!

531
00:23:03,673 --> 00:23:06,259
Have you forgotten your past mistakes?

532
00:23:06,343 --> 00:23:08,136
She keeps downing them.

533
00:23:08,637 --> 00:23:09,721
Are you okay?

534
00:23:09,805 --> 00:23:11,223
-Yeah, it's tasty.
-Really?

535
00:23:12,307 --> 00:23:15,393
What percent alcohol are you going for?

536
00:23:15,477 --> 00:23:16,520
I'd better keep it light.

537
00:23:17,229 --> 00:23:18,772
I can handle it even if it's strong.

538
00:23:19,606 --> 00:23:20,732
You're acting tough.

539
00:23:22,943 --> 00:23:23,819
I'm all talk.

540
00:23:24,820 --> 00:23:26,404
You need to drink what I make.

541
00:23:26,488 --> 00:23:29,574
-I'm ready to get black-out drunk today.
-You'll drink it all?

542
00:23:30,575 --> 00:23:32,160
I think I'll need a month to drink it all.

543
00:23:32,744 --> 00:23:33,703
One glass a day.

544
00:23:33,787 --> 00:23:35,997
I'm the only eternal single who drinks.

545
00:23:36,081 --> 00:23:36,915
You are.

546
00:23:36,998 --> 00:23:38,375
So I feel a bit…

547
00:23:39,292 --> 00:23:41,586
It's a bit disappointing
that no one else can drink.

548
00:23:41,670 --> 00:23:43,004
-We're all lightweights.
-Yeah.

549
00:23:44,131 --> 00:23:45,674
I'll drink with you when we get back.

550
00:23:45,757 --> 00:23:46,800
-Really?
-Yes.

551
00:23:46,883 --> 00:23:48,718
