what he was in for.

555
00:23:57,269 --> 00:23:59,813
Don't say that so cheerfully!

556
00:24:00,355 --> 00:24:03,150
<i>But I was happy that he offered</i>

557
00:24:03,233 --> 00:24:04,484
<i>to drink with me.</i>

558
00:24:04,568 --> 00:24:06,319
<i>-That's what she wanted to hear.</i>
<i>-Yes.</i>

559
00:24:06,820 --> 00:24:09,489
I wanted to ask you something earlier.

560
00:24:10,073 --> 00:24:12,367
