-Yes?

561
00:24:12,450 --> 00:24:14,578
could you tell which one belonged to whom?

562
00:24:15,328 --> 00:24:16,788
Well, that…

563
00:24:16,872 --> 00:24:17,956
What do you call it?

564
00:24:18,039 --> 00:24:19,499
-The strap?
-Yeah, that's right.

565
00:24:19,583 --> 00:24:22,544
When I saw it, I knew it was yours.

566
00:24:22,627 --> 00:24:25,797
