as I was bringing it.

567
00:24:25,881 --> 00:24:27,507
They were all obvious.

568
00:24:27,591 --> 00:24:28,508
But…

569
00:24:29,217 --> 00:24:30,135
That's why…

570
00:24:31,469 --> 00:24:33,263
I made up my mind as soon as I saw it.

571
00:24:33,930 --> 00:24:35,432
I knew I wanted to pick the strap.

572
00:24:37,058 --> 00:24:38,643
I wanted to get to know you.

573
00:24:42,856 --> 00:24:44,232
Is this a budding romance?

574
00:24:45,358 --> 00:24:46,234
It's going well.

575
00:24:48,528 --> 00:24:49,738
I was really grateful.

576
00:24:50,488 --> 00:24:52,324
-It was nice to get picked early.
-Right.

577
00:24:52,407 --> 00:24:54,743
You picked it when it was obviously mine,

578
00:24:54,826 --> 00:24:55,744
and it was a relief.

579
00:24:56,244 --> 00:24:57,495
So you knew.

580
00:24:58,455 --> 00:24:59,956
You knew I picked yours on purpose.

581
00:25:03,752 --> 00:25:05,754
We made this in-house.

582
00:25:05,837 --> 00:25:06,922
Thank you.

583
00:25:07,881 --> 00:25:10,133
It looks good.
I was craving something like this.

584
00:25:10,217 --> 00:25:12,052
-I was so hungry.
-Me too.

585
00:25:14,346 --> 00:25:15,680
"Reveal your age."

586
00:25:15,764 --> 00:25:17,349
<i>-Now?</i>
<i>-Just between them.</i>

587
00:25:17,432 --> 00:25:19,184
<i>-Nice timing.</i>
-I'm so curious.

588
00:25:20,143 --> 00:25:21,228
Who should go first?

589
00:25:23,521 --> 00:25:25,690
Were you born in 2000?

590
00:25:25,774 --> 00:25:27,776
-Yes, I was.
-I got it right?

591
00:25:27,859 --> 00:25:28,693
Yes, I'm 26 years old.

592
00:25:31,112 --> 00:25:32,697
I'm 27 years old. I was born in 1999.

593
00:25:32,781 --> 00:25:33,865
-Oh, you're 27?
-Yes.

594
00:25:34,491 --> 00:25:35,784
It's a one-year difference.

595
00:25:35,867 --> 00:25:37,327
-That's not much.
-Right.

596
00:25:37,410 --> 00:25:39,371
Call me<i> nuna</i>.

597
00:25:40,330 --> 00:25:41,498
You want me to call you <i>nuna</i>?

598
00:25:42,165 --> 00:25:43,833
Yeah, I like that term.

599
00:25:43,917 --> 00:25:45,377
-Really?
-I like hearing that.

600
00:25:46,378 --> 00:25:47,587
I prefer that to my name.

601
00:25:48,255 --> 00:25:49,381
I'll call you that from now on.

602
00:25:50,507 --> 00:25:52,509
I sense some spark between them.

603
00:25:52,592 --> 00:25:54,552
They're flirting like crazy.

604
00:25:54,636 --> 00:25:55,720
Oh, Han-ju!

605
00:25:58,974 --> 00:26:01,476
<i>I don't mind that he's younger.</i>

606
00:26:01,559 --> 00:26:02,644
Maybe I am

607
00:26:03,603 --> 00:26:04,646
