682
00:28:54,357 --> 00:28:57,068
The guys that I've been fangirling over…

683
00:28:57,152 --> 00:28:58,903
-They're younger?
-Right, they're younger.

684
00:28:58,987 --> 00:29:03,074
So I thought that might be why

685
00:29:03,158 --> 00:29:06,244
I'm more drawn to younger guys.

686
00:29:06,995 --> 00:29:10,457
But even I feel like maybe it's time

687
00:29:10,540 --> 00:29:13,126
to stop being such a fangirl.

688
00:29:13,209 --> 00:29:16,171
Fangirling is the kind of thing
you do when you're young.

689
00:29:16,254 --> 00:29:18,423
-Don't you think so?
-But…

690
00:29:19,257 --> 00:29:21,593
I don't see it that way.

691
00:29:21,676 --> 00:29:22,552
