00:31:36,352 --> 00:31:39,772
Because of that, I kind of…

738
00:31:41,316 --> 00:31:44,402
I wanted to talk with her.

739
00:31:44,986 --> 00:31:47,238
-So that's who I wanted to talk to most.
-Oh, really?

740
00:31:53,578 --> 00:31:56,456
Jung-yun said that he was

741
00:31:57,081 --> 00:31:59,751
a bit more interested in talking to Su-ji.

742
00:32:00,335 --> 00:32:02,670
When he told me that so openly,

743
00:32:02,754 --> 00:32:05,381
it was like he confirmed

744
00:32:05,465 --> 00:32:09,636
what I had kind of suspected.

745
00:32:09,719 --> 00:32:12,555
