746
00:32:13,556 --> 00:32:15,475
The conversation flowed well,

747
00:32:15,558 --> 00:32:19,687
but I don't think I felt much attraction.

748
00:32:19,771 --> 00:32:22,899
Right now, I want to get to know Su-ji.

749
00:32:23,608 --> 00:32:24,484
Come on.

750
00:32:25,443 --> 00:32:28,112
-He didn't need to tell her that.
-He didn't.

751
00:32:28,196 --> 00:32:30,990
-He basically rejected her.
-He did.

752
00:32:31,074 --> 00:32:33,910
Saying what isn't necessary
is a classic eternal single move.

753
00:32:33,993 --> 00:32:35,495
Right, this is <i>Better Late Than Single</i>.

754
00:32:37,330 --> 00:32:40,041
-I mean, if he feels that certain…
-Yeah, that's fair.

755
00:32:40,124 --> 00:32:41,250
If he's that sure…

756
00:32:41,334 --> 00:32:43,294
ONE-ON-ONE DATE
JAE-SEO, SOO-HYUN

757
00:32:43,378 --> 00:32:45,296
<i>-Hello.</i>
<i>-Hello.</i>

758
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:49,092
This workshop is called "Color Hunting."

759
00:32:49,175 --> 00:32:51,302
Pick a color that you like,

760
00:32:51,386 --> 00:32:53,012
and color this in like so

761
00:32:53,096 --> 00:32:57,308
-to make your own personal palette.
-Okay.

762
00:32:58,434 --> 00:33:01,062
