00:35:48,479 --> 00:35:50,940
REVEAL YOUR AGE TO YOUR DATE

823
00:35:51,023 --> 00:35:52,483
<i>-It's the age reveal.</i>
-Our ages?

824
00:35:55,027 --> 00:35:56,154
-I was born
-Yes.

825
00:35:57,196 --> 00:35:58,030
in 1998.

826
00:35:58,614 --> 00:35:59,615
I'm 28 years old.

827
00:36:00,533 --> 00:36:02,410
I'm 32 years old.

828
00:36:02,493 --> 00:36:04,162
-Really?
-I was born in 1994.

829
