830
00:36:07,081 --> 00:36:08,124
You're wrong.

831
00:36:08,749 --> 00:36:09,959
I started in 2023.

832
00:36:10,042 --> 00:36:11,377
No, I mean me.

833
00:36:11,460 --> 00:36:12,461
-What?
-I started in 2011.

834
00:36:12,545 --> 00:36:14,005
Oh, I thought you were talking about me.

835
00:36:14,088 --> 00:36:15,173
-You started in 2011?
-Yes.

836
00:36:16,507 --> 00:36:18,050
-You started in 2023?
-Yeah, 2023.

837
00:36:18,134 --> 00:36:19,510
It's a 12-year difference?

838
00:36:19,594 --> 00:36:21,637
<i>Oh, he finished high school early.</i>

839
00:36:21,721 --> 00:36:23,681
<i>And Soo-hyun enrolled</i>
<i>a little later than her peers.</i>

840
00:36:23,764 --> 00:36:26,559
<i>It's surprising for a four-year age gap.</i>

841
00:36:26,642 --> 00:36:27,518
You started in 2011?

842
00:36:27,602 --> 00:36:28,769
Yeah.

843
00:36:30,146 --> 00:36:32,648
This is a bit too…

844
00:36:32,732 --> 00:36:34,066
It's a bit of a shock.

845
00:36:34,734 --> 00:36:36,319
-Now, I'm worried.
-Why?

846
00:36:36,402 --> 00:36:38,196
Everyone will find out when we get back.

847
00:36:38,279 --> 00:36:41,532
I was worried even before I came here

848
00:36:41,616 --> 00:36:43,367
