849
00:36:43,451 --> 00:36:45,661
No, Jae-seo, you're good.

850
00:36:45,745 --> 00:36:47,371
Wait. What's happening?

851
00:36:47,455 --> 00:36:49,165
Did his chair break?

852
00:36:49,248 --> 00:36:51,042
-It won't hold much longer.
-Red alert!

853
00:36:51,125 --> 00:36:52,752
Oh, no!

854
00:36:53,586 --> 00:36:54,670
"Should work out," they said.

855
00:36:55,379 --> 00:36:56,881
<i>Watch out, Jae-seo!</i>

856
00:36:56,964 --> 00:36:59,383
<i>-Stop leaning!</i>
<i>-Why are you leaning so far back?</i>

857
00:36:59,467 --> 00:37:00,509
-No.
-Stop!

858
00:37:00,593 --> 00:37:02,261
Wouldn't he feel that something's off?

859
00:37:02,762 --> 00:37:04,722
I love that we can talk about this.

860
00:37:04,805 --> 00:37:08,851
The older you get… Hold on.

861
00:37:13,940 --> 00:37:14,941
Oh my gosh!

862
00:37:17,985 --> 00:37:18,986
This is really…

863
00:37:21,405 --> 00:37:22,365
That's so…

864
00:37:23,658 --> 00:37:25,243
-Wait a minute.
-Give me a break.

865
00:37:25,326 --> 00:37:28,204
It'd have been better if he fell.

866
00:37:28,287 --> 00:37:29,997
-Why hold it like a harp?
-Maybe.

867
00:37:30,081 --> 00:37:31,958
But hey, it made Soo-hyun laugh.

868
00:37:32,875 --> 00:37:33,960
<i>She's dying.</i>

869
00:37:34,543 --> 00:37:35,503
It's just so…

870
00:37:36,045 --> 00:37:37,421
-What do I do?
-What do we do?

871
00:37:37,505 --> 00:37:39,465
I need to apologize.

872
00:37:39,548 --> 00:37:41,592
-This seems right up her alley.
-Yeah, it's good.

873
00:37:41,676 --> 00:37:42,885
At least she's laughing.

874
00:37:42,969 --> 00:37:44,428
Why'd you do that to the chair…

875
00:37:45,263 --> 00:37:46,931
-Oh my gosh.
-Come on.

876
00:37:47,014 --> 00:37:48,724
Is it really that funny?

877
00:37:50,268 --> 00:37:52,395
Oh, this is how it's meant to fit.

878
00:37:52,478 --> 00:37:54,397
-Stop it.
-It was like this…

879
00:37:55,398 --> 00:37:57,775
What if this actually makes her
fall for him?

880
00:38:00,027 --> 00:38:01,821
I wanted to figure out

881
00:38:01,904 --> 00:38:04,824
if it was attraction or friendship,

882
00:38:04,907 --> 00:38:08,786
but we didn't need
to have that talk at all.

883
00:38:08,869 --> 00:38:11,372
I realized instantly we're just friends.

884
00:38:11,455 --> 00:38:14,000
-Oh, really?
-She's made a fun new friend.

885
00:38:14,083 --> 00:38:15,167
-Right.
-She has.

886
00:38:15,251 --> 00:38:16,127
It's a fun memory.

887
00:38:16,210 --> 00:38:18,754
Soo-hyun had given him half a vote.

888
00:38:18,838 --> 00:38:21,716
He was her second choice,
but now he's off the list.

889
00:38:22,300 --> 00:38:24,760
<i>-I think this couple will be fun to watch.</i>
<i>-It's got a nice vibe.</i>

890
00:38:24,844 --> 00:38:26,387
<i>Seung-hyun and Jeong-eun.</i>

891
00:38:26,470 --> 00:38:28,055
-Hello.
-Hello.

892
00:38:28,681 --> 00:38:30,266
Have you handled a camera before?

893
00:38:30,850 --> 00:38:31,809
-Not film cameras…
-Not like this.

894
00:38:31,892 --> 00:38:34,020
-Just a phone camera, right?
-Yes.

895
00:38:34,103 --> 00:38:36,897
