899
00:38:48,534 --> 00:38:49,827
<i>-Shall we set out?</i>
<i>-Yes.</i>

900
00:38:49,910 --> 00:38:50,828
<i>This is a nice activity.</i>

901
00:38:50,911 --> 00:38:52,621
<i>-It is.</i>
<i>-Where should we go for a pretty shot?</i>

902
00:38:52,705 --> 00:38:54,498
Shall we take it from this angle?

903
00:38:54,582 --> 00:38:55,916
Hold on. This…

904
00:38:56,667 --> 00:38:58,961
We might end up
buying a film camera after this.

905
00:38:59,045 --> 00:38:59,962
-We might.
-Right?

906
00:39:00,046 --> 00:39:02,548
-But let's see the results first.
-The results first?

907
00:39:04,133 --> 00:39:05,384
I've only used a disposable camera…

908
00:39:05,468 --> 00:39:06,302
-Oh my.
-Jeez.

909
00:39:07,094 --> 00:39:08,095
