910
00:39:08,596 --> 00:39:09,722
Did I break it?

911
00:39:09,805 --> 00:39:10,765
No.

912
00:39:10,848 --> 00:39:12,183
I think you can put it back in.

913
00:39:12,808 --> 00:39:13,809
