914
00:39:14,352 --> 00:39:15,561
-I think it's this.
-Right.

915
00:39:16,771 --> 00:39:17,855
There we go.

916
00:39:17,938 --> 00:39:20,524
Jeong-eun's doing all the work.

917
00:39:20,608 --> 00:39:23,361
Didn't he say he was into photography?

918
00:39:23,444 --> 00:39:24,862
-It's a cute shot. Want to see?
-Yes.

919
00:39:24,945 --> 00:39:25,821
Does it look okay?

920
00:39:26,947 --> 00:39:27,948
-It looks good.
-Shall I pose?

921
00:39:28,032 --> 00:39:29,950
-Yes, go over.
-I'm not sure about the height.

922
00:39:30,868 --> 00:39:32,203
-It's good!
-It's okay?

923
00:39:32,286 --> 00:39:34,205
-Yeah, I think so.
-You do?

924
00:39:34,789 --> 00:39:36,123
