925
00:39:38,626 --> 00:39:40,252
-I'll take it now.
-You need to wind the film.

926
00:39:40,336 --> 00:39:41,379
Oh, right.

927
00:39:43,172 --> 00:39:44,673
-I'm going to click now.
-Okay.

928
00:39:44,757 --> 00:39:45,800
-Come on.
-I'd better run.

929
00:39:47,510 --> 00:39:48,344
Oh, gosh.

930
00:39:48,427 --> 00:39:49,762
-Ready? Shall we do a V?
-Yeah.

931
00:39:49,845 --> 00:39:50,888
Yeah, let's do a V.

932
00:39:53,140 --> 00:39:55,601
<i>-Looking good!</i>
<i>-They're both so smiley.</i>

933
00:39:55,684 --> 00:39:57,978
-I'm not sure about the results.
-I wonder how it came out.

934
00:39:58,562 --> 00:40:00,815
-I wish we could see it.
-I'm so curious.

935
00:40:01,482 --> 00:40:02,566
-It's going well.
-It is.

936
00:40:02,650 --> 00:40:04,735
This might bring them closer together.

937
00:40:05,236 --> 00:40:07,196
-Shall we take one of the flowers?
-Good idea.

938
00:40:07,279 --> 00:40:08,823
You try it.

939
00:40:11,575 --> 00:40:13,702
Why is it stuck?

940
00:40:14,620 --> 00:40:15,996
Is it broken inside?

941
00:40:16,080 --> 00:40:17,540
Do you think it's broken?

942
00:40:17,623 --> 00:40:19,959
-Maybe the earlier shot didn't work too.
-You're right.

943
00:40:20,042 --> 00:40:22,378
Darn it. I did think something was off.

944
00:40:22,461 --> 00:40:23,754
I didn't hear the shutter sound.

945
00:40:26,132 --> 00:40:27,091
What? You fixed it!

946
00:40:27,758 --> 00:40:30,094
-Nice. Yeah.
