949
00:40:34,473 --> 00:40:35,933
-Let's take another one as we go.
-Good idea.

950
00:40:36,016 --> 00:40:37,726
-Jeong-eun's pulling all the weight.
-She is.

951
00:40:39,562 --> 00:40:40,855
Did it work? Wait… What…

952
00:40:40,938 --> 00:40:42,189
